8C1F951063","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Mix bacterial precipitate in phosphate buffer in incubation, and dilute it. OD600 of the bacterial liquid used for next measurement is 0.15.<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":822741,"guid":"AFF5428996DB4D2EA1BDC856CCD56D86","previous_id":822740,"previous_guid":"AF47BD4C6AC640AB9A32095505ACD4C0","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"667A8F54285941AD898279FFC01B215A","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"4193987CA8924C8CA57F17C80CD78AC7","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\"><a href=\"\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">UV-Vis test I. <\/span><\/a><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Test one experimental group together with 3 different controls. Record the absorption value every 300 seconds, 12 times in total.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><ol style = \"list-style-type: decimal;\"><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;\">95\u03bcL bacterial liquid which express target protein, 5\u03bcL cefazolin(final concentration is 250\u03bcM);<\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;\">95\u03bcL beta-lactamase(final concentration is decided by characteristic of enzyme), 5\u03bcL cefazolin(final concentration is 250\u03bcM);<\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;\">95\u03bcL bacterial liquid which is transferred with blank vector, 5\u03bcL cefazolin(final concentration is 250\u03bcM);<\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;\">95\u03bcL phosphate buffer, 5\u03bcL cefazolin(final concentration is 250\u03bcM). Then plot the UV-vis spectroscopy with time.<\/li><\/ol><\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","